name: Slashed Ace - Rise - 1/1 Edition
description:
My HEN Genesis

In life we all must rise to face our challenges
Rise to confront our fears
Rise above the day to day bullshit
Rise over our personal struggles
Rise from the ashes after we burn

If we can learn to stand together, we can rise together

Rise - V.
-to assume an upright position
-to return from death
-to take up arms
-to respond warmly
-to appear above the horizon
-to ascend
-to become elated
-to increase in fervor or intensity
-to exert oneself to meet a challenge
-to come into being

CHRONO: {DXLII}
